uientry.unicode: Use this panel to merge armies, fleets or to move agents.

Exchange||Select a unit, agent or troop and click here to move them to the other army or navy.||If you have a selection from each army or navy, this button will swap them over.||You can also move them by simply dragging and dropping the cards.||Once a panel is full, it means that army or navy has its maximum amount of units and you cannot add any more.
uientry.s:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("unit_exchange"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("ExchangeSelected") end
function OnUpdatePulse(time_ms)
local valid_selection = parent:LuaCall("HasValidSelection") local current_state = this:CurrentState()
if valid_selection == true and current_state == "inactive" then this:SetState("normal") elseif valid_selection == false and current_state ~= "inactive" then this:SetState("inactive") end
end

local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("unit_exchange"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("FinaliseExchange") end

local this = UIComponent(Address) local parent = UIComponent(this:Parent("unit_exchange"))
function OnSelect() parent:LuaCall("CancelExchange") end

uientry.unicode: When this timer runs out, the battle will be fought according to the default setting. || The default setting is the button that is highlighted.
